    dc:title "Three new species of the genus Ocychinus (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae) from China" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3884893>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3884895>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3884885>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3884897>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3884881> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3884893>
    dc:description "FIGURES 42–45. Ocychinus. 42 head and pronotum of O. muotuoensis; 43 head and pronotum of O. smetanai; 44 abdominal tergite IV of O. muotuoensis; 45 abdominal tergite IV of O. smetanai. Scale bars = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3884893/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3884895>
    dc:description "FIGURES 46, 47. Head and pronotum of Ocychinus. 46 O. huanghaoi; 47 O. bohemorun Smetana, 2010. Scale bars = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3884895/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3884885>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15–20. Adult habitus of Ocychinus. 15 O. bohemorun Smetana, 2010 (paratype); 16 O. paramerosus Smetana, 2003 (holotype); 17 O. businskius (Smetana, 2010) (paratype); 18 O. kalabi Smetana, 2003 (holotype); 19 O. businskorum Smetana, 2003 (holotype); 20 O. yeti (Dvořák, 2003). Scale bars =2mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3884885/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3884897>
    dc:description "FIGURES 48, 51. Ocychinus. 48 head and pronotum of O. meridionalis Smetana, 2003; 49 head and pronotum of O. monticola Smetana, 2003; 50 pronotum of O. xizangensis Smetana, 2003; 51 pronotum of O. kalabi Smetana, 2003. Scale bars = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3884897/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3884881>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9–14. Adult habitus of Ocychinus. 9 O. tibetanus Smetana, 2003 (paratype); 10 O. frater Smetana, 2008 (holotype); 11 O. meridionalis Smetana, 2003 (paratype); 12 O. monticola Smetana, 2003 (holotype); 13 O. xizangensis Smetana, 2003 (holotype); 14 O. sichuanensis Smetana, 2003 (holotype). Scale bars =2mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3884881/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

